node.text: @positiveleepeilin sure! Please do inform the time - I am in mumbai , India.
@positiveleepeilin so do we! 😘

🎥 My first livestream storytelling came and went... just like this long weekend! 🤪⁠⠀
.⁠⠀
Shout out to @celine_tan @melodybay @belandbray for sharing with your friends... we had around 40+ children join in the story sharing 🧒🏻👶🏻👦🏻I could almost hear some of the camera-change countdowns from my home! 😍⁠⠀
.⁠⠀
For those who overslept, you can watch the rerun on my IGTV 😴😜📺⁠⠀
.⁠⠀
🎁I'm doing a giveaway as I know things have been a bit difficult lately and I want to send you a bit of sunshine! I’m picking one lucky viewer to win a set of soybean crayons which I bought from Crayon Castle in Taiwan PLUS a limited edition notebook by Jimmy Liao 🖍️🏰📒 I bought these from my last holiday in Taiwan ✈️🇹🇼🏖️⁠⠀
.⁠⠀
📩 To take part, email me at positiveleepeilin@gmail.com to subscribe to my newsletters and I’ll be picking a lucky viewer from there. Giveaway closes this Saturday and I'll announce the winner on Sunday, 31 May ☀️⁠⠀
.⁠⠀
Would you be keen on more online storytelling sessions? 📖📚💬Does it matter if it's a live stream or a pre-recorded video? Let me know if it matters in the comments below, so I can figure out what to create next! 👇🏻⁠

.
.⁠⠀

@positiveleepeilin try out both and find which one strikes a better chord? 😊
@belandbray Good point! Contemplating which story next from my stockpile of books. I miss the library and bookshops!
@positiveleepeilin so do we! 😘

Thank you for the lovely stories this morning Peilin! Bray woke us up at 9am and asked is it time yet, is it time yet? 😆 The kiddos loved it live and asked me to type faster to reply you😅😂...but we think recorded is fine too, then we can replay on repeat! Heehee...to more stories!😍😍❤️❤️
@jinghan_911 awesome lah!😄
@belandbray Haha @positiveleepeilin is awesome!
@jinghan_911 told y'all so, eh? 😍😍
@jinghan_911 I think you were there too ya? In case you need Peilin's email to join her giveaway 😉
@hiadamroberts Adam! I remember you from TIL and haven’t seen your name come up in ages! I hope you’re well ☺️
How fun this must have been! :)
@daisyfaithart I see you have more swimsuits for me to ogle over, Daisy! This was a fun morning! 😍
What a fun idea 🤩
@jinghan_911 No worries at all, my intention is to spend time with your girls, so you can do other things if you want! Thank you for your inputs on live vs prerecording!

Hi Peiling! Thank you for the awesome stories you brought to my girls earlier today! Though I gotta confess that I was cooking in the kitchen, my girls told me they enjoyed the session and are looking forward to another session! It doesn’t really matter to us if it’s a live or pre-recorded session as long as it’s an interesting one... But I’ll think a live one will prolly be more engaging especially if you have an interactive component like what you had before you started your story-telling and yes, before I went off to the kitchen.. :p Thank you again! :)))
@kaylem_kacey Hi mama kk (how should I address you? 🙈) ok, sounds like both options work! 👍🏽
Thank you for doing this, my boys enjoyed the session very much :) And we don’t mind either live or pre-recorded!
@ruhaansbookshelf Hihi Ruhaan, they’re cutouts! 😊 Join us on our next session, if you can! Would love to have you!
@positiveleepeilin sure! Please do inform the time - I am in mumbai , India.
Wow! Are those cutouts or puppet?
@celine_tan_ ✨ Ohoh, one more question! Does the book itself matter? Like a popular children’s book versus one that is lesser known?
Loved it! Thanks Peilin and please do more live sessions! The interactivity makes it really fun for the kids 👍🏼☺️❤️
We enjoyed it too! Gotta leave earlier due to HBL! Will rewatch it IGTV!!!
